					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">No, attributes are applied per 32 pixels. You could update it per 16 pixels, but that'd be just way too complicated. Or more complicated than 32 pixels. 1 byte is stored for a 4x4 tile chunk. 2 bits for each 2x2 section.</div>

					
